description: The investment seeks investment results that correspond to the price and yield performance, before fees and expenses, of the MorningstarÂ Emerging Markets Factor Tilt Hedged IndexSM. The index (i) reflects the performance of a selection of companies that, in aggregate, possess greater exposure to size and value factors relative to the Morningstar Emerging Markets Index, and (ii) hedges the currency-related risk of the securities included in the index against the U.S. dollar on a monthly basis. The fund invests at least 80% of its total assets in the securities of the index and in ADRs and GDRs based on the securities in the index. The fund is non-diversified.
name: FlexShares Currency Hedged Morningstar EM Factor Tilt Index Fund
